# bibleg

Unofficial Bible API in Python

## Usage

```python
>>> from bibleg import get_text

>>> get_text("John 11:35")
'Jesus wept.'

>>> get_text("Gen 1:1")
'In the beginning, God created the heavens and the earth.'
```
